Package neureka.calculus

Class Function.Detached

java.lang.Object
neureka.calculus.Function.Detached
Enclosing interface:
Function
public static class Function.Detached
extends java.lang.Object
This static nested class acts as namespace for pre-instantiated Function instances which are configured to not track their computational history. This means that no computation graph will be built by these instances. ( Computation graphs in Neureka are made of instances of the "GraphNode" class... )
